  "description": "<i>Slither</i> is similar in nature to the hit arcade game <a href=\"https://www.mobygames.com/game/centipede_\">Centipede</a> by Atari.  You control your snake as it <i>slither's</i> around the screen.  Where this game differs greatly from Centipede is that you can shoot in 4 different directions at the same time to take out the baddies trying to hunt you down.  The <i>bad</i> snakes hunting you down will appear from various angles on the screen, often several at a time.  The game was bundled with Coleco's <i>Roller Controller</i> and can't be played without it.",
